docs/development/HOWTO-add-model.md:107:### 3. Build the GGML graph implementation
docs/development/HOWTO-add-model.md:109:This is the funniest part, you have to provide the inference graph implementation of the new model architecture in `src/llama-model.cpp`.
docs/development/HOWTO-add-model.md:110:Create a new struct that inherits from `llm_graph_context` and implement the graph-building logic in its constructor.
docs/development/HOWTO-add-model.md:112:Then, in the `llama_model::build_graph` method, add a case for your architecture to instantiate your new graph-building struct.
docs/development/HOWTO-add-model.md:116:Note: to debug the inference graph: you can use [llama-eval-callback](/examples/eval-callback/).
