ggml/src/ggml-cann/aclnn_ops.h:947: *              - src0: [D, M, A, 1], where A is the number of experts
ggml/src/ggml-cann/aclnn_ops.h:949: *              - ids : [K, N],       where K is the number of experts each token is routed to
ggml/src/ggml-cann/aclnn_ops.h:950: *              - dst : [M, K, N, 1], output tensor storing the result of expert × token multiplication
ggml/src/ggml-cann/aclnn_ops.h:957: * @param dst The destination tensor where the expert-weighted token outputs are stored.
